title: [Whistler's Pass, Subalpine]
description: The trail moves down the side of a ridge and across a rounded meadow covered in deep green grasses.  The sky stretches out in an enormous sea of black framed by the ghostly forms of the moonlit, snow-capped peaks.

The trail moves down the side of a ridge and across a rounded meadow covered in deep green grasses.  The sky stretches out in an enormous sea of blue framed by the craggy peaks that surround the pass.
